member.summary:
   Looks up a localized string similar to Game over. This is your data:
Total time used: {0:hh':'mm':'ss'.'fff}
Puzzles count: {1}
Average time used: {2:hh':'mm':'ss'.'fff}
Correct rate: {3:P} ({4}/{5}).

